title: Unvanquished Alpha 31
description:
A team-based, fast-paced, FPS/RTS hybrid game that pits aliens against humans.

Unvanquished is a futuristic team-based and fast-paced multiplayer first person shooter with real time strategy elements that pits technologically advanced humans against hordes of highly adaptable aliens. The player can choose from either team, providing a fresh gameplay experience on both sides of the conflict. The rare melee vs. ranged gameplay is what makes this game so interesting and complex.

The game is free open source software and runs on Linux, Windows and Mac. The torrent contains the portable version with binaries for all platforms. No need to install, just download and run.
